<file path="README.md">
# ZEVO — Power Everything.
```
A premium electronics e-commerce website built with HTML & CSS. Dark-themed & visually rich.
```


## Tech Stack

- **HTML5** — Semantic elements (`<nav>`, `<main>`, `<header>`, `<footer>`, `<section>`)
- **CSS3** — Custom properties, Flexbox, Grid
- **JavaScript** — Lenis smooth scroll (CDN) + nav scroll effect only
- **Fonts** — Google Fonts: Outfit (headings), Inter (body), JetBrains Mono (accents)
- **Icons** — Font Awesome 6 (CDN)


## File Structure

```
/
├── favicon.svg
├── index.html
├── README.md
├── css/
│   ├── main.css              ← Reset, variables, typography
│   ├── components.css        ← Buttons, cards, badges, forms
│   ├── nav.css               ← Header & navigation
│   ├── footer.css            ← Footer styles
│   ├── home.css              ← Homepage sections
│   ├── shop.css              ← Shop + category pages
│   ├── product.css           ← Product detail pages
│   ├── cart.css              ← Cart page
│   ├── checkout.css          ← Checkout + confirmation
│   ├── about.css             ← About page
│   ├── contact.css           ← Contact page
│   ├── auth.css              ← Login & register
│   └── profile.css           ← Profile, wishlist, 404
├── js/
│   └── main.js               ← Lenis init + nav scroll toggle
├── media/
│   ├── hero/
│   ├── categories/
│   ├── products/
│   └── team/
└── html/
    ├── shop.html
    ├── cart.html
    ├── wishlist.html
    ├── checkout.html
    ├── confirmation.html
    ├── about.html
    ├── contact.html
    ├── 404.html
    ├── categories/
    │   ├── smartphones.html
    │   ├── laptops.html
    │   ├── audio.html
    │   ├── smartwatches.html
    │   ├── cameras.html
    │   └── accessories.html
    ├── products/
    │   ├── nexus-ultra-pro.html
    │   ├── apex-book-pro.html
    │   ├── pulse-buds-pro.html
    │   └── zwatch-ultra.html
    └── account/
        ├── login.html
        ├── register.html
        └── profile.html
```


## Pages

| Page | Description |
|------|-------------|
| Homepage | Hero, categories, featured products, brand manifesto, trust badges, newsletter |
| Shop | Sidebar filters + 16-product grid |
| Category | Category hero banner + filtered product grid |
| Product Detail | Image gallery, specs, pricing, add to cart |
| Cart | 2 sample items + order summary |
| Checkout | Shipping & payment forms + summary sidebar |
| Confirmation | Order confirmed success page |
| Wishlist | 4-column product grid with add to cart |
| About | Mission, values, team, CTA |
| Contact | Contact info + form |
| Login | Centered auth card |
| Register | Centered auth card |
| Profile | Sidebar + orders table |
| 404 | Large error code with glow effect |


## How to Run

1. Install the **Live Server** extension in VS Code
2. Right-click `index.html` → **Open with Live Server**


## Design

- **Theme:** Dark mode (#0A0A0A background)
- **Accent:** Yellow (#FACC15)
- **Typography:** **Outfit** for headings, **Inter** for body, **JetBrains Mono** for labels
- **Currency:** INR / Rs.
- **Target viewport:** Desktop (1280px+)



